Step 1:
    Run ez_setup.py with python
Step 2:
    From your favorite command line utulity, try executing the following as administrator 
    easy-install openpyxl
    easy-install xlrd    
Step 3:
    Done!
    
    
Troubleshooting:
If you have troubles installing/running easy-install (steps 1 and 2) try looking here http://packages.python.org/distribute/easy_install.html
